---
title: Hoisin Beef Tacos with Sesame Slaw
description: This quick family dinner packs bold flavours inspired by Taiwanese beef scallion pancakes into a taco. Crunchy slaw tossed in a creamy sesame dressing tops hoisin-glazed beef for a sure-fire fam fave!
